description: Divisor-or-multiple permutation of squarefree numbers: a(0) = 1, and for n >= 1, a(n) is either the least divisor of a(n-1) not already present, or (if all divisors already used), a(n) is obtained by iterating the map x -> x*A053669(x), starting from x = a(n-1), until x is found which is not already present in the sequence.
